  "title": "Body Therapist Reflexologist",
  "description": "<p>• Massage customers and administer other body treatments</p>\n<p>• Understand the needs and expectations of each client, recommend body treatments, and provide the most effective wellness service to the client.</p>\n<p>• Knowledge of TCM Cupping, Scraping (GuaSha), and Tuina will be a plus point</p>\n<p>• Maintain a high level of professional customer service.</p>\n<p>• Create an excellent guest experience through a friendly and helpful attitude.</p>\n<p>• Responsible for maintaining cleanliness and neatness of the facilities and treatment room.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>• Preferably with a Diploma certification </p>\n<p>• Effective communication skills.</p>\n<p>• Minimum 3 years or more of relevant experience</p>\n<p>• Require to work 6 days a week 10 am to 10 pm.</p>\n<p>• Able to work on weekends / public holidays</p>\n<p>•Good Hygiene practice, patience, and a good sense of responsibility</p>",
